<section class="tw xbox font-sm" id="T3"><h3 class="obj_head">Appendix A.</h3>
<div class="caption p"><p id="P37">Bivariate Correlations Between Athlete Status and Exercise
Behavior</p></div>
<div class="tbl-box p" tabindex="0"><table class="content" frame="hsides" rules="none">
<colgroup span="1">
